summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of North and West Seventy-fourth Street from Winora Avenue to Eighth Avenue Northwest et al in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete sidewalks and under Ordinance No. 23920, creating Local Improvement District No. 2317 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing the delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
